===Etymology===
From {{OF.}} ''[[ableté]]'' (French ''[[habileté]]'', earlier spelling ''[[habilité]]'' with [[silent]] ''h''), from {{L.}} ''[[habilitas]]'' [[aptitude]], ability, from ''[[habilis]]'' apparently.  See [[able]].

